{"type": "article", "id": 49429, "title": "一款可以各种调试的吊灯，灵感来自马戏团表演｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-23T23:27:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 767, "name": "家具设计"}, {"id": 47211, "name": "OS & OOS"}, {"id": 47212, "name": "Aggestrup"}, {"id": 47213, "name": "TRIMM Copenhagen"}, {"id": 36505, "name": "Oblure"}, {"id": 47214, "name": "Carbono Design"}, {"id": 28151, "name": "Arflex"}, {"id": 6314, "name": "如恩设计"}, {"id": 47215, "name": "Vinicius Siega"}, {"id": 47216, "name": "Jette Scheib"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/2018012020124554o3yNs6g9EXx0dJ.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>“摇篮”系列家具 Cradle Collection by 如恩设计 for Arflex</h3><p>Arflex 自创立之初就一直致力于与建筑师的合作。在受邀为品牌设计一款扶手椅时，如恩很自然地选择从构造的角度入手。设计概念源于沙发的结构本身，采用经典的三角形并通过多次重复制造出有趣的形态。</p><p>串联着的皮带加固了沙发结构，也支撑着布面的靠背和坐垫，包围成摇篮的形状。与遮盖沙发结构从而营造漂浮感的手法相比，“摇篮”沙发选择将支撑结构暴露出来，体现出做工与优雅的细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201447Ck23T9nDxStF5ImL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.046997\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201321ygo0CiqUlujBIect.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801202013298B4RFUHhtDr5zwyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.948276\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201339Z9ipl5NTSA8b3OvM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.483019\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>New Furniture Collection by Vinicius Siega for Carbono Design</h3><p>巴西家具设计师 Vinicius Siega 最近为 Carbono Design 推出了一个新的家具系列，融合极简主义和热带风情。整个系列包括椅子，桌子和花瓶等，材质、色彩在每一件作品中的混搭，创造出视觉上的轻重之感。Vinicius Siega 融合了巴西核桃木、彩绘饰面钢铁材料以及纺织布料等材料，但最终的表达形式仍然偏向于简练干净。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201512zNYmXpPrs6E49aId.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201517nUcmFsMXpu6hqW0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.412500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201517J6tUj0gXbCnKY1WA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201520Jab6VjngKF4UE2xz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.327344\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018012020152281z7kHiy30QvJKDe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.297656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/vinicius-siega-launches-new-furniture-collection-carbono-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Trapeze Pendant by Jette Scheib for Oblure</h3><p>童年去马戏团参观的经历留给德国设计师 Jette Scheib 很深的印象。他以此为灵感，为瑞典品牌 Oblure 设计了吊灯 Trapeze，整个灯的形态就像是马戏团表演时，演员和观众互动时摇摆身体的样子。</p><p>半圆形的固定装置允许每一边旋转 360 度，不仅改变了灯光的投射方式，还改变了吊灯的外观。Jette Scheib 的设计很灵活，允许每盏 Trapeze 吊灯融入一个更大的系统，多个吊灯可以以不同的组合方式使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j05360ercew&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201715kxJ6fN2lW8rPsGY4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201715rOG9hQsy0u8wRnJj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.848000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201716Iys2SQnrTqkjLPfx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201717rpzPGxVDJTbB8cEM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801202017196RaE57LdJewTCV9h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.271000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201719Spg1LAQq3t7CMjdX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/trapeze-pendant-by-jette-scheib-for-oblure/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></p><h3>Colorful Outdoor Mattresses by TRIMM Copenhagen</h3><p>丹麦户外家具品牌 TRIMM Copenhagen 推出了今年的春季新款，一个新的户外坐垫系列。它不像我们常见的户外家具，而是可以平铺在地板上的床垫和靠垫。如果你不想直接躺在地上，也可以平配一个尺寸标准的木质托架，当然也可以自己 DIY。</p><p>这个系列有两种尺寸选择，内置智能磁铁，易于连接在一起。它允许用户自定义配置各种样式，适合非正式的亲友聚会，坐起来很舒服。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201839LJyrSKlV2QAsqUut.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801202018404kaQ3PyZXwJp7s9H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201845vch5BVXb6oLKa7W4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.789844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201856ngyXaBcAxYs8V2fK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120201903h3xoHqQYfCM8K1dn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>#80 by Aggestrup</h3><p>灵活性已经是工作场所家具十分看重的要素，就像在家里使用多用途家具一样。人们现在把更多的时间花在开放的办公室、机场、候车室和大堂上，很容易从混乱中得到过度刺激，并增加与他人的互动。最近，Aggestrup 设计了一系列座椅，引入了公众场景中经常缺少的隐私级别，以此来帮助保持注意力集中。</p><p>80 号系列旨在简化我们的生活，并改变我们如何思考和使用私人和公共座椅。这一系列与丹麦的经验丰富的工匠合作，每件作品都是手工制作而成。座椅视觉上感觉很轻盈，绑带缠绕在木框上，增加了一层温暖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202018XljN7vFecfGUq5as.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801202020193iDGdN6Lz7Ek9j2M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.311719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202019uZqMx1UIgpCljmzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202020N7dtn29vpuwoPSsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.307813\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801202020349e6w8o1G7zLIQpPg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Matrix: A Light and Bench Built From a Grid Structure by OS &amp; OOS</h3><p>埃因霍温设计二人组 OS &amp; OOS 设计了一个由金属网格系统制成的灯和长凳 Matrix 系列。设计师使用三维网格结构，由薄薄的钢条制成，允许不同的方式配置，构筑成各种类型的结构。华夫饼似的网格结构允许用户透视内部的光源，若隐若现，当灯点亮时，很像个艺术作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202117yvg3dCEbZ6uUNmJf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505469\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202119hQzc4XdsLKgmW1Av.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.204687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202119fAmgBZ3UCSKadbxQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202120iBfK7MGtZYz8bXNP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180120202128VHaMPL0zlm1gtGx4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.505469\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}